<CategoryLayout
  title="Translation Services Dubai | MOJ Certified Legal Translation | OnlineTranslation.ae"
  description="Professional MOJ-certified translation services in Dubai. Legal documents, personal certificates, corporate filings, Golden Visa packages, and attestation services. 43+ languages, same-day delivery available."
